profile:
West Birch is your local choice for carpentry and handyman services. We service retail, commercial, and residential clients, in the greater Victoria area. We specialize in jobs from 1 hour to 5 days in duration. 

We look forward to helping  you with tasks such as drywall, painting, concrete, caulking and many more. 

How are we different? We take a sustainable approach to the industry. We try and source materials both locally, and from vendors that focus on providing sustainable building materials and we also recycle materials where we can.
